snippet.title: AMBER HEARD TELLS JOHNNY DEPP "NO ONE WILL BELIEVE YOU" IN NEW AUDIO || ANALYSIS
snippet.description:
Hi guys, 

I know that the audio was released on the 5th of February, I did film this the following day, but I have only just found the time to edit and upload it. 

In this video I am discussing the audio that was obtained by DAILY MAIL of a phone conversation between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp. Here is a link to the originial article in which I retrieved the audio. - 

https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7966723/Amber-Heard-ridicules-Johnny-Depp-claiming-hes-domestic-violence-victim.html

Thank you for your continued support of my content over the years, this audio is quite distressing, but I hope you enjoy my breakdown of it.

AOV

Twitter and instagram: @Autumn On Venus
